        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 1 at 5:32PM MDT by NWS Great Falls MT</headline>
        <description>At 532 PM MDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Choteau, moving northwest at 10 mph.

HAZARD...Nickel size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Choteau, Farmington, and Bynum.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
